frameDefinitions: These are words relating to emptying containers and clearing areas of some substance or items.
A Location is filled or covered with the Theme.
An Item is in a state of dryness.
A Phenomenon, which may be an activity, state or object, is purposefully hidden from the awareness of a potential Cognizer.
A Protagonist has (or does not have) a Weapon.
frameExamples: The players <t>emptied</t> the bucket over his head.
The waters of the bay <t>teemed</t> with fish.
Few people would use ATMs if the content of their transaction was <t>secret</t> from their bank and there was no paper trail verifying the transaction. .
Apparently, the suspect is <t>armed</t> with a shotgun.
listRoleDefinitions: The <fen>Agent</fen> is the entity that does the emptying.
The <fen>Theme</fen>, when overtly expressed, invariably occurs in a PP Complement headed by 'of'.
The <fen>Source</fen> is the region or container which is emptied of something.  In this frame, the <fen>Source</fen> occurs as an NP Object.
The <fen>Cause</fen> is the non-sentient force which instigates the emptying.
The time at which the emptying takes place.
The location where the emptying takes place.
The <fen>Theme</fen> covers or fills the <fen>Location</fen>.  This role most frequently occurs in a PP Complement headed by with or in.
<fen>Location</fen> is the object or area that the <fen>Theme</fen> fills or covers.  This frame element generally occurs as the External Argument.
The period of time during which the the Abounding_with event occurs.
The <fen>Item</fen> exists in a state of dryness.
The <fen>Phenomenon</fen> is the activity, state or object that is purposefully hidden from the awareness of a potential cognizer.
A period of <fen>Time</fen> during which the <fen>Phenomenon</fen> is hidden from the awareness of potential cognizers.
The destructive device that the <fen>Protagonist</fen> has with them.
The time at which the <fen>Protagonist</fen> carries a <fen>Weapon</fen>.
The location where a <fen>Protagonist</fen> carries a <fen>Weapon</fen>.
listRoleExamples: <fex>A basic washing</fex> can degrease your workclothes.
The prisoners were deloused <fex>in June and August</fex>.
The waters of the bay teemed <fex>with fish</fex>.
<fex>The walls</fex> crawled with nanite surveillance probes.
There was stuff in there that was 'secret' <fex>in the 1980s</fex>, but has since become pretty common knowledge.
